Package tumble.game

All major game elements.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Camera
    Represents the area of the map shown to players at a given moment.
    Game
    Represents a Tumble game.
    Item
    Represents a collectible item with a rectangular hitbox.
    Map
    Represents the map that the player can explore.
    MovableRectangle
    Represents a movable rectangle.
    Platform
    Represents a stationary platform.
    Player
    Represents a movable ellipse with basic physics and rectangular collision detection.
    Vine
    Represents a patch of vine.
